<h2>Roblox Clothing Copier Early Beta</h2>
<h3>Setup Instructions</h3>
<p>This only works if you are on computer. If you aren't on computer then this wont work.<br></p>
<p>1. Get the bookmark <b>simply</b> by dragging the <b>'Copy Clothing'</b> button to your bookmark bar. 
<br>
<br>
<a id="bookmark"
href="PasteJavaHere"

 onclick="copyToClip()" class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary btn-icon rounded-pill">
<span class="btn-inner--text">Copy Clothing</span></a></p><br>
<p>If you don't see the bookmark bar then press <b>'CTRL+SHIFT+B'</b> then drag the button in an empty space.<br></p>
<p>2. Go to an <b>Clothing</b> on <b>Roblox Catalog.</b><br></p>
<p>3. Press on the bookmark and paste in the ID of the Clothing in the popup.</p>
<p>4. A new tab should open and a clothing template should appear.</p>
